==[[Scottish Gaelic]]==

===Adjective===
'''Bàn'''
* [[White]], pale, [[fair]].
* Of [[hair]], fair, [[blond]]; ''"Dh'ionndrainn mi mo leannan bàn" ("I longed for my fair-haired [[sweetheart]]")''.

